{"logo":"https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=8&quality=60&sec=1534503471&di=3bede26c736a9806c2ca3cf631c954f5&src=http%3A%2F%2Fh.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fxiaodu%2Fpic%2Fitem%2Fc2fdfc039245d688f3171888acc27d1ed21b2480.jpg","summary":"广东文艺职业学院(Guangdong Literary & Art Vocational College)简称“广文艺”，是全国文联系统唯一一所高职院校，位于广东省广州市，是公办综合性艺术类高等院校，也是广东文化大省建设九大工程之一。学院前身是由叶剑英元帅1950年3月创办的“华南人民文学艺术学院”，校名由毛泽东主席题写；1985年，更名为华南文艺业余大学；2004年定名为广东文艺职业学院。据2017年11月学校官网信息显示，学院校园分为番禺主校区、郭兰英艺术分院、海联路校区，共占地188.7亩；教学仪器设备总值2354.35万元，馆藏纸质图书28.58万册，电子图书45万册；设有8个教学单位，26个专科专业；拥有全日制在校生近4228人，教职员工340人，其中专任教师223人。","tags":["艺术类","专科","公办"],"attrs":{"创建时间":"1951","所在地区":"广州市番禺区市广路242号","院校隶属":"广东省文联","重点学科数":"1"},"imgs":["https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534503471&di=034625857041b86e1997a122736fcded&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3440966790%2C3851800112%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534503471&di=fa6e3babd5af7f560c3dfc889b609979&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3706684243%2C834363689%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534503471&di=1113fca91eae96376daf132990b814ef&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3579812409%2C3829243432%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534503471&di=941e06f22450688265b40ca3a73b3bd0&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3603649724%2C811100808%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534503471&di=500e6e190ce67d722ab7492e77c8f84d&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3555469377%2C718775258%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic